#################################################
#                   User errors                 #
#################################################

You need all input files in this directory to reproduce errors 

Error in input json file:

    bash run.sh input_fail 0 50

also when no such json file

More than one base inserted in one place:

    bash run.sh multins_fail 0 50

Error in sequence input file:

    bash run.sh phex 0 seq_fail phex.csv

also when no such seq file 

Error in staple csv file:

    bash run.sh phex 0 seq phex_fail.csv

also when no such staple file

Seequence does not match staple list:

    bash run.sh phex 0 seq_notmatch phex.csv
    
More than one scaffold chain:

    bash run.sh addscaf_fail 0 50

Insertion or deletion in single-stranded region:

    bash run.sh ssdelet_fail 0 50

Single-strande staple:

    bash run.sh ssolig_fail 0 50

Cicular staple:

    bash run.sh circ_fail 0 50
